		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p rend="align(center)"><placeName>New York</placeName> <date>Octob. 3<hi rend="sup">rd</hi> 1864</date></p>
				<p><addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
				<p><add>Hebrew</add></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><persName role="author">M. Light</persName></p>
				<p><add>Hebrew</add></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><persName role="author">M. Light</persName></p>
				<p><add>&#63;</add></p>
			<pb n="Envelope"/>
				<p><addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
				<p><placeName>Walnut Street</placeName></p>
				<p><placeName>near 13th Street</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philadelphia Pa</placeName></p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York</placeName>&#44; <date>October 3&#44; 1864</date>.</p>
				<p><addressee>Reverend Isaac Leeser</addressee>&#44; <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>&#44;</p>
				<p>Honored Sir&#58;</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Herewith a draft for &#36;21. for the holiday prayer books<lb/> in ordinary binding&#44; and send me by return a set of holiday prayer<lb/> books for &#36;21. and a set of gilt.  And if you have no gilded ones&#44;<lb/> then send me a set for &#36;25.50.&#44; as <sic>wellas</sic> several Portuguese prayer<lb/> books.  I live opposite the new Portuguese synagogue.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">You may also send me a large set &#40;I mean large octavo&#41; in<lb/> gilt&#44; if you have no small ones.</p>
			<p rend="indent(9)">Respectfully&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(10)"><persName role="author">M. Light</persName></p>
				<p>I have received Italian ethrogim&#44; and I sell them wholesale or retail.<lb/>  Perhaps you will be able to sell several boxes for me&#44; if only several<lb/> ethrogim for your congregation.  Send me....&#40;German note about sub&#45;<lb/>scribers to &#8220;Occident&#8221;&#41;.</p>
		</body>
